messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
I don't have access to your current location. Could you provide your latitude and longitude so I can help identify the city?
I don't know my latitude and longitude either.

Unfortunately, without your latitude and longitude or any other location clues, I can't determine your current city. If you can provide any additional details (like a nearby landmark, address, or postal code), I’d be happy to help!
I really don't have any other details at all.

I understand, but without any location information—such as coordinates, address, or nearby landmarks—I’m unable to determine your city. If you’re on a device with internet access, you might try searching “What city am I in?” on a search engine or using a geolocation website that can detect your approximate location. Let me know if you’d like help with anything else!
